            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>爱吃烤生蚝～</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/food2.4clhccquq2.webp'
            alt='Food photo 2'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>爱吃炒花甲～</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/food3.2a5ooas9ol.webp'
            alt='Food photo 3'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>爱吃烤串～</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/food4.7lkl90eccf.webp'
            alt='Food photo 4'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>爱吃炝锅烩面～</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class='rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4'>
      <h3 class='mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-foreground'>Karaoke Nights</h3>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-3'>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/ktv.9gx61n20aj.webp'
            alt='Karaoke photo 1'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>MYGO版本《蝴蝶》</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/ktv.36263rd6gs.webp'
            alt='Karaoke photo 2'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>《樱之诗》</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/ktv.32ik61k3r0.webp'
            alt='Karaoke photo 3'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>《悠久之翼》</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class='rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card p-2'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='https://pic.hana0721.top/ktv.1hst6kmwak.webp'
            alt='Karaoke photo 4'
            class='aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-md object-cover'
            />
          <figcaption class='px-1 pt-1.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>《Always in my heart》</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
  <h2 id='steam'>🎮 Steam<a class='anchor' href='#steam'>#</a></h2>
  <p>
    我在 Steam 上主要玩的游戏包括《杀戮尖塔》《饥荒联机版》《求生之路》，也会玩各种 3A 和一些团建游戏，比如《恐鬼症》《前方高能》《致命公司》。另外我有一点收集癖，收藏了不少 Galgame，翻库存的时候观感非常舒服。
  </p>
  <p>
    《杀戮尖塔》是我投入最多的游戏，累计时长已经超过 2000 小时。当前个人最好成绩是 Silent 在 SL 玩法下 179 连胜、在 NOSL 玩法下 10 连胜；我也把相关攻略持续整理到了 <a href='/collection/sts-guide'>Slay The Spire 系列攻略</a>。最近我也在玩《杀戮尖塔 2》，欢迎同好来一起联机交流。
  </p>
  <p>
    《饥荒联机版》这边我主要玩女武神，也做过一篇比较高质量的攻略，放在 B 站：<a href='https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1MwGNz6EGF/'>女武神原版攻略合集</a>。至于《求生之路》，平时主要打战役或者药抗，比较菜，不要喷我🙅。
  </p>
  <p>
    我的 Steam 个人主页在这里：<a href='https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561199033212179/'>菊花花zako</a>，欢迎来加好友扩列，一起开黑。
  </p>
  <a
    href='https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561199033212179/'
    target='_blank'
    rel='noopener noreferrer'
    aria-label='Steam 个人主页截图'
  >
    <DeferredImage
      src='https://pic.hana0721.top/steam.7pvxaowx7.webp'
      alt='Steam 个人主页截图'
      class='my-4 rounded-xl border border-border'
      />
  </a>
  <section class='not-prose mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4'>
    <h3 class='mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-foreground'>Screen Shot</h3>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3'>
      <figure class='overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-border/70 bg-card'>
